description: An exciting curbside dining experience you won't soon forget! The Absolute BBQ Express features a delicious quick-service menu of BBQ favorites prepared with only the finest ingredients.  Inside, you'll see a state-of-the-art stainless steel kitchen complete with ultra-modern amenities to create fresh hot delicious food service. We've even gone the extra mile and imported a wood burning pizza oven!
name: Absolute BBQ Express
